      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        The Complete Seller Disclosure Checklist for Queensland
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queensland's statutory disclosure framework, introduced under the Property Law Act 2023, is now a central part of every home sale. Here is the full checklist of what you must disclose, what you should disclose, and the common traps that cause contracts to fall over.
      </p>
    </div>
